(31890, 'Glozithro 500mg vial', 'جلوزيثرو 500 مجم فيال', '', '94', 'Azithromycin 500mg', 'Rameda > glory medical', 'Vial', 'فيال', 'مضاد حيوى واسع المدى يستخدم فى علاج العديد من العدوى البكتيرية', 'Macrolide antibiotic', '500mg', 'Azithromycin should be used only to treat or prevent infections that are proven or strongly suspected to be caused by susceptible bacteria in order to prevent the development antimicrobial resistance and maintain the efficacy of azithromycin [FDA label].
